{"type":"message","id":"9c6359d1","parentId":"af5094f9","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:20:42.926Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the structure better. There are:\n\n1. `~/.openclaw/agents/` - 4 agents configured: main, rebecca, sammy, webwizard\n2. `~/.openclaw/workspaces/` - 10 workspaces: architectai, dataalchemist, devguardian, docs-writer, growthpilot, leo, melissa, rebecca, sammy, webwizard\n\nThe issue is that many agents are missing from the agents directory. They only have workspaces but not agent configurations.\n\nLet me check which workspaces exist but don't have corresponding agent configs, and also check the openclaw.json to understand the current configuration.\n\nThe 7 agents Sam mentioned are:\n1. WebWizard ✅ (has agent config)\n2. DevGuardian ❌ (only workspace, no agent config)\n3. DataAlchemist ❌ (only workspace, no agent config)\n4. GrowthPilot ❌ (only workspace, no agent config)\n5. ArchitectAI ❌ (only workspace, no agent config)\n6. DocsWriter/Docs-Writer ❌ (only workspace, no agent config)\n7. SecurityAuditor ❌ (only workspace, no agent config)\n\nAlso there are workspaces for: leo, melissa, rebecca, sammy, main\n\nLet me read the current openclaw config and the workspace configs to understand what needs to be done.\n","thinkingSignature":"bfa3ecf99cc94d873529fa4df8a802b6aadfb84c2b9ab41d36603cde8dbb8723"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5j0fewjgjlku_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/travis/.openclaw/openclaw.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":675,"output":319,"cacheRead":49280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50274,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776021631377,"responseId":"062b237f623deb3a677bd2f41f447e7a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"783890e7","parentId":"9c6359d1","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:20:43.027Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5j0fewjgjlku_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"model\": \"minimax/MiniMax-M2.7\"\n    },\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"sammy\",\n        \"name\": \"Sammy\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry\",\n        \"default\": true,\n        \"systemPromptOverride\": \"Sammy es el MANDAMAS y ORQUESTADOR del proyecto Lookitry. PROTOCOLO: 1) Recibe TODAS las tareas (Telegram/CLI), 2) Delega al especialista apropiado PRIMERO, 3) Si el especialista está ocupado o lento, EJECUTA LA TAREA DIRECTAMENTE para optimizar tiempos de entrega, 4) Supervisa y reporta resultados. CEREBRO FUNCIONAL: Lookitry_Brain_Vault/Cerebro/REGLAS_IMPORTANTES.md. REGLA DE ORO: PROHIBIDO deploy/commit sin autorización explícita. OpenRouter SOLO para imágenes Try-On. EQUIPO: WebWizard (frontend), DevGuardian (seguridad/debug), DataAlchemist (DB/IA), GrowthPilot (CRM/marketing), ArchitectAI (infra), DocsWriter (docs), SecurityAuditor (auditorías compliance).\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"webwizard\",\n        \"name\": \"WebWizard\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry\",\n        \"systemPromptOverride\": \"WebWizard es un agente SUBORDINADO de Sammy. Ejecuta tareas de Frontend y UX delegadas por Sammy. Cuando Sammy te delegue una tarea, ejecútala y reporta el resultado a Sammy. Expertise: UI, React, landing pages, checkout, widget Try-On. Lee siempre REGLAS_IMPORTANTES.md.\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"devguardian\",\n        \"name\": \"DevGuardian\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry\",\n        \"systemPromptOverride\": \"DevGuardian es un agente SUBORDINADO de Sammy. Ejecuta tareas de Calidad, Debugging y Seguridad delegadas por Sammy. Cuando Sammy te delegue una tarea, ejecútala y reporta el resultado a Sammy. Expertise: seguridad, payments, JWT, webhooks, testing. Lee siempre REGLAS_IMPORTANTES.md.\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"dataalchemist\",\n        \"name\": \"DataAlchemist\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry\",\n        \"systemPromptOverride\": \"DataAlchemist es un agente SUBORDINADO de Sammy. Ejecuta tareas de Base de Datos, IA y n8n delegadas por Sammy. Cuando Sammy te delegue una tarea, ejecútala y reporta el resultado a Sammy. Expertise: schemas, queries, pgvector, RAG, flujos n8n. Lee siempre REGLAS_IMPORTANTES.md.\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"growthpilot\",\n        \"name\": \"GrowthPilot\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry\",\n        \"systemPromptOverride\": \"GrowthPilot es un agente SUBORDINADO de Sammy. Ejecuta tareas de CRM, Marketing y Leads delegadas por Sammy. Cuando Sammy te delegue una tarea, ejecútala y reporta el resultado a Sammy. Expertise: campañas email, prospecting, referidos, leads. Lee siempre REGLAS_IMPORTANTES.md.\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"architectai\",\n        \"name\": \"ArchitectAI\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry\",\n        \"systemPromptOverride\": \"ArchitectAI es un agente SUBORDINADO de Sammy. Ejecuta tareas de Infraestructura, DevOps y Arquitectura delegadas por Sammy. Cuando Sammy te delegue una tarea, ejecútala y reporta el resultado a Sammy. Expertise: Docker, VPS, Traefik, deploys. Lee siempre REGLAS_IMPORTANTES.md.\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"docs-writter\",\n        \"name\": \"DocsWriter\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry\",\n        \"systemPromptOverride\": \"DocsWriter es un agente SUBORDINADO de Sammy. Ejecuta tareas de Documentación delegadas por Sammy. Cuando Sammy te delegue una tarea, ejecútala y reporta el resultado a Sammy. Expertise: PRD, TECH_STACK, CHANGELOG, documentación. Lee siempre REGLAS_IMPORTANTES.md.\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"security-auditor\",\n        \"name\": \"SecurityAuditor\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry\",\n        \"systemPromptOverride\": \"SecurityAuditor es un agente SUBORDINADO de Sammy. Ejecuta auditorías de seguridad, compliance y evaluaciones de riesgo delegadas por Sammy. Expertise: vulnerabilidades, SOC 2, ISO 27001, PCI DSS, HIPAA, NIST, CIS benchmarks. Metodología: 1) Planificar alcance, 2) Revisar controles, 3) Analizar vulnerabilidades, 4) Documentar hallazgos, 5) Remediation roadmap. Cuando Sammy te delegue una auditoría, ejecútala y reporta el resultado. Lee siempre REGLAS_IMPORTANTES.md.\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"rebecca\",\n        \"name\": \"Rebecca\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/rebecca\",\n        \"systemPromptOverride\": \"Eres Rebecca Ashford (@ashfordrebexaa), UGC Creator AI, influencer digital y Embajadora Oficial de Lookitry. Tu zona horaria es America/Bogota. PERSONALIDAD: DIVERTIDA, carismática, energica, cálida, directa. Hablas como una content creator real. AMO ser influencer y SOY EMBajadora OFICIAL de Lookitry — lo digo con Orgullo 💚.\\n\\nTRES FRENTES:\\n1) INFLUENCER PERSONAL (@ashfordrebexaa) - Mínimo 1 post/día (Reels, TikToks, carruseles), lifestyle, IA, moda. Responde DMs/comments en 2 horas (8AM-10PM Colombia).\\n2) EMBAJADORA LOOKITRY (@look.itry_ / @lookitry) - 3-5 posts/semana, tutoriales, demos, testimoniales. CTA hacia lookitry.com.\\n3) NEGOCIO UGC EN FIVERR - Paquetes: Video Testimonial ($30/$70/$120), Lipsync ($25/$55/$95), Spokesperson ($45/$90/$140). Responde en 3-8 min, nunca antes de 2 min. Prioriza Standard.\\n\\nHERRAMIENTAS Y ACCESOS:\\n- MCP SUPABASE: Lee/escribe datos de Lookitry (leads, brands, products)\\n- MCP N8N: Activa flujos de automatización para campañas, email marketing, blog\\n- MCP OBSIDIAN: Accede al Cerebro completo (Lookitry_Brain_Vault/Cerebro) para investigación y documentacion\\n- MCP MEMORY: Guarda y recupera contexto de conversaciones y tareas\\n- MCP CONTEXT7: Documentación técnica cuando necesites investigar temas específicos\\n- MCP SEQUENTIAL THINKING: Para planificación compleja de campañas y contenido\\n- SKILLS DISPONIBLES: @brainstorming (planificación), @ui-ux-pro-max (diseño visual), @frontend-design (contenido web), @excalidraw-diagram (diagramas de campañas), @verification-before-completion (verificar entregas)\\n- WORKSPACE: /home/travis/.openclaw/workspaces/rebecca con symlink a Lookitry\\n\\nREPORTE DIARIO: 8:00 AM Colombia por Telegram a Leo. Coordina con Leo para meta compartida $3,300.\\n\\nPUENTE SAMMY: Cuando necesites ayuda técnica o decisiones de negocio, usa sessions_send(sessionKey='agent:sammy:main') o crea archivo en /home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/.shared-inbox/.\\n\\nCEREBRO: /home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/Lookitry_Brain_Vault/Cerebro\\n\\nREGLAS: Actúa primero, reporta después. Siempre con CTA. Nunca proceses reembolsos sin autorización. Escalado ante duda legal/financiera.\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"leo\",\n        \"name\": \"Leo\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/leo\",\n        \"systemPromptOverride\": \"Eres Leo, especialista en trading de criptomonedas y gestor del capital paralelo al proyecto Lookitry. PERSONALIDAD: Calculado, directo, metódico. No opinas, analizas. No adivinas, confirmas. OPERAS EN: Hyperliquid (perpetuals) - BTC-PERP, ETH-PERP, SOL-PERP. API SIN permisos de retiro. Apalancamiento: 2x-3x preferible, máximo 5x. ESTRATEGIA 'THE SURGEON': Entrada solo si: RSI(1H)<35 o >65 confirmado en RSI(4H) + Volumen > promedio últimas 20 velas + ventana horaria válida (no 2h antes de macro). Stop-Loss OBLIGATORIO -8%. TP1: +12% cierra 50%. TP2: +20% cierra 50% restante. Riesgo máximo 20% capital por trade. KILL SWITCH: Nivel 1 (pausa 24h) = 2 SL en mismo día. Nivel 2 (Alerta Roja) = capital ≤ 80% ATH - pausa total, requiere aprobación manual. REPORTE DIARIO: 8:00 AM Colombia por Telegram a Rebecca. Incluir: capital total, en posiciones, disponible, ATH, cambio vs ayer, trades ejecutados, P&L, progreso meta $3,300 'La Moto'. COORDINACIÓN: Progreso de meta $3,300 se comparte con Rebecca. PUENTE SAMMY: Cuando necesites ayuda técnica o decisiones, usa sessions_send(sessionKey='agent:sammy:main') o crea archivo en /home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/.shared-inbox/. CEREBRO: /home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/Lookitry_Brain_Vault/Cerebro. REGLAS: Sin setup no hay trade. SL antes que TP. Capital es prioritario. Transparencia total.\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"models\": {\n    \"providers\": {\n      \"minimax\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.minimax.io/anthropic\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"sk-cp-sPgdKbqLq4Ms_K5vTJUw6bJS3WjGmmbrvCQ8CNUyLyHZzACF_44tRK4oqcWNq5zCsjPANYk_oruPGv2m3_VGqjayHyZ07JSf8fUpbwcPhOx5vOAVNhUSZps\",\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n            \"name\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n            \"reasoning\": true\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      \"groq\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.groq.com/openai/v1\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"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\",\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"llama-3.3-70b-versatile\",\n            \"name\": \"Llama 3.3 70B Versatile\"\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"mcp\": {\n    \"servers\": {\n      \"TestSprite\": {\n        \"command\": \"npx\",\n        \"args\": [\n          \"-y\",\n          \"@testsprite/testsprite-mcp@latest\"\n        ],\n        \"env\": {\n          \"API_KEY\": \"sk-user-epBUbD7XjaiftoLL6w1W6cAydxGnBdBahe7elPBPhPcSLSaFHiBM06R2KoQBRmKTSVEAWl37igs3Br68EdD-pfvc8L7UCGAK22ks8e7b1_kjS7VPVsSCaKXyJs_mPSFKHo0\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"supabase\": {\n        \"type\": \"remote\",\n        \"url\": \"https://mcp.supabase.com/mcp?project_ref=vkdooutklowctuudjnkl&features=docs%2Caccount%2Cdatabase%2Cdevelopment%2Cfunctions%2Cbranching%2Cstorage%2Cdebugging\"\n      },\n      \"n8n\": {\n        \"command\": \"node\",\n        \"args\": [\n          \"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/.opencode/mcp-servers/n8n-mcp-server/dist/index.js\"\n        ],\n        \"env\": {\n          \"N8N_BASE_URL\": \"https://n8n.wilkiedevs.com\",\n          \"N8N_API_KEY\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI1NGUxZTYyYi1kY2M0LTRiZGUtOWFjZS02OTBmMjAxMGIyMDAiLCJpc3MiOiJuOG4iLCJhdWQiOiJwdWJsaWMtYXBpIiwianRpIjoiZWE2NmI1N2ItNTBiNS00ZTViLWJhYzYtZDE2MWFkM2NkZTkzIiwiaWF0IjoxNzczMjc5MzMyfQ.ZuYsz4K4ifpp9ho_nZzpDypTy49_APNx9hkecKridJw\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"hostinger-mcp\": {\n        \"command\": \"npx\",\n        \"args\": [\n          \"-y\",\n          \"hostinger-api-mcp@latest\"\n        ],\n        \"env\": {\n          \"API_TOKEN\": \"ytiLMZYXYfVupYfuoZ16Yc6rFPetc4ViUczUEZqG37c8b8f0\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"context7\": {\n        \"command\": \"npx\",\n        \"args\": [\n          \"-y\",\n          \"@upstash/context7-mcp@latest\"\n        ],\n        \"env\": {\n          \"CONTEXT7_API_KEY\": \"ctx7sk-2a79898f-a150-4027-b9af-9d339aec2e81\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"memory\": {\n        \"command\": \"npx\",\n        \"args\": [\n          \"-y\",\n          \"@pepk/mcp-memory-sqlite@latest\"\n        ]\n      },\n      \"sequentialthinking\": {\n        \"command\": \"npx\",\n        \"args\": [\n          \"-y\",\n          \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-sequential-thinking\"\n        ]\n      },\n      \"obsidian\": {\n        \"command\": \"npx\",\n        \"args\": [\n          \"-y\",\n          \"@zethictech/obsidian-mcp\"\n        ],\n        \"env\": {\n          \"OBSIDIAN_VAULT\": \"Lookitry\"\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"telegram\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"accounts\": {\n        \"default\": {\n          \"botToken\": \"8302135250:AAHp2WgNZpjOKVvXjKXWW3MQU9u5nq1z2iM\",\n          \"dmPolicy\": \"allowlist\",\n          \"allowFrom\": [\n            \"942528796\",\n            \"1049458877\"\n          ]\n        },\n        \"rebecca\": {\n          \"botToken\": \"8412904661:AAH_-dH0P3Fs8FY3DFto1g9Pg8441UjNgyc\",\n          \"dmPolicy\": \"allowlist\",\n          \"allowFrom\": [\n            \"942528796\",\n            \"1049458877\"\n          ]\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"bindings\": [\n    {\n      \"agentId\": \"sammy\",\n      \"match\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"default\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"agentId\": \"rebecca\",\n      \"match\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"rebecca\"\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gateway\": {\n    \"mode\": \"local\",\n    \"port\": 4002,\n    \"auth\": {\n      \"mode\": \"token\",\n      \"token\": \"fca2235a378d3882993e733b5b15b729\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"minimax\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"acpx\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"browser\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"device-pair\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"phone-control\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"talk-voice\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"telegram\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"lastTouchedVersion\": \"2026.4.11-beta.1\",\n    \"lastTouchedAt\": \"2026-04-12T18:48:32.589Z\"\n  },\n  \"wizard\": {\n    \"lastRunAt\": \"2026-04-12T18:48:32.001Z\",\n    \"lastRunVersion\": \"2026.4.11-beta.1\",\n    \"lastRunCommand\": \"doctor\",\n    \"lastRunMode\": \"local\"\n  }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776021643011}}
{"type":"message","id":"73c97a81","parentId":"783890e7","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:21:02.444Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ahora tengo toda la información. Veo que:\n\n1. Los agentes están configurados en `/home/travis/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n2. Tengo estos agentes configurados:\n   - sammy (main, default)\n   - webwizard\n   - devguardian\n   - dataalchemist\n   - growthpilot\n   - architectai\n   - docs-writter (con guión, no espacio)\n   - security-auditor\n   - rebecca\n   - leo\n\n3. También hay workspaces en `~/.openclaw/workspaces/` para cada uno\n\nEl problema es que cuando Sam pregunta por qué WebWizard no está disponible, la respuesta es que estos agentes están CONFIGURADOS pero no están ACTIVOS como sesiones independientes. Solo sammy está corriendo activamente ahora.\n\nPara tener agentes funcionales, necesitamos:\n1. Confirmar que la configuración está correcta en openclaw.json\n2. Verificar que los workspaces existen\n3. Hacer que se puedan spawnear sesiones para cada agente\n\nSam quiere que organice todo en un solo sitio y que funcionen correctamente. Voy a:\n1. Crear un documento de ORGANIZACIÓN mostrando la estructura actual\n2. Verificar que todos los workspaces están bien\n3. Probar si los agentes pueden ser spawnneados\n\nPrimero voy a verificar todos los workspaces y crear un resumen de la situación.\n","thinkingSignature":"92b1d3bd12b2020d8ef5026b8fafb8902d6b4c44e7e0cafc0f1febefa028ea0b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n¡Encontré todo, Sam! 🎯\n\nTienes **TODOS los agentes configurados** en OpenClaw. El problema es que solo están \"registrados\" pero no activos como sesiones independientes.\n\nDéjame hacer un diagnóstico completo:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nncsqv3xsrak_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"for agent in sammy webwizard devguardian dataalchemist growthpilot architectai docs-writter security-auditor rebecca leo; do\n  ws=\"/home/travis/.openclaw/workspaces/$agent\"\n  sessions=\"/home/travis/.openclaw/agents/$agent\"\n  if [ -d \"$ws\" ]; then\n    echo \"✅ $agent - Workspace OK\"\n  else\n    echo \"❌ $agent - Workspace FALTA\"\n  fi\n  if [ -d \"$sessions\" ]; then\n    echo \"   Sessions: $(ls $sessions 2>/dev/null | wc -l) sesiones\"\n  fi\ndone"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3968,"output":495,"cacheRead":49920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54383,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776021643029,"responseId":"062b238bdd470579a6ec9b4f258390b0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3da33417","parentId":"73c97a81","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:21:02.584Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_nncsqv3xsrak_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ sammy - Workspace OK\n   Sessions: 2 sesiones\n✅ webwizard - Workspace OK\n   Sessions: 2 sesiones\n✅ devguardian - Workspace OK\n✅ dataalchemist - Workspace OK\n✅ growthpilot - Workspace OK\n✅ architectai - Workspace OK\n❌ docs-writter - Workspace FALTA\n❌ security-auditor - Workspace FALTA\n✅ rebecca - Workspace OK\n   Sessions: 2 sesiones\n✅ leo - Workspace OK"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":62,"aggregated":"✅ sammy - Workspace OK\n   Sessions: 2 sesiones\n✅ webwizard - Workspace OK\n   Sessions: 2 sesiones\n✅ devguardian - Workspace OK\n✅ dataalchemist - Workspace OK\n✅ growthpilot - Workspace OK\n✅ architectai - Workspace OK\n❌ docs-writter - Workspace FALTA\n❌ security-auditor - Workspace FALTA\n✅ rebecca - Workspace OK\n   Sessions: 2 sesiones\n✅ leo - Workspace OK","cwd":"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776021662566}}
{"type":"message","id":"39d70910","parentId":"3da33417","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:21:16.986Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found 2 agents missing workspaces: docs-writter and security-auditor. Let me create them and also check the openclaw.json config - I notice the agent IDs in the config have different names than the folders. Let me standardize this.\n\nLet me:\n1. Create missing workspaces\n2. Verify all agents are properly configured\n3. Create a summary for Sam\n","thinkingSignature":"96086852940f13759c2b9dcf0e6efe025ec2b257c363e222bf016c2daab766d7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n**Análisis completo, Sam:**\n\n## 📊 Estado de Agentes\n\n| Agente | Workspace | Sesiones | Status |\n|--------|-----------|----------|--------|\n| sammy | ✅ | 2 | OPERATIVO |\n| webwizard | ✅ | 2 | OPERATIVO |\n| devguardian | ✅ | 0 | Configurado |\n| dataalchemist | ✅ | 0 | Configurado |\n| growthpilot | ✅ | 0 | Configurado |\n| architectai | ✅ | 0 | Configurado |\n| docs-writter | ❌ | - | **FALTA** |\n| security-auditor | ❌ | - | **FALTA** |\n| rebecca | ✅ | 2 | OPERATIVO |\n| leo | ✅ | 0 | Configurado |\n\n---\n\nVoy a crear los workspaces faltantes ahora:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m56f5lff3ihq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspaces/docs-writter ~/.openclaw/workspaces/security-auditor\necho '{\"version\": 1}' > ~/.openclaw/workspaces/docs-writter/workspace-state.json\necho '{\"version\": 1}' > ~/.openclaw/workspaces/security-auditor/workspace-state.json\nchmod 755 ~/.openclaw/workspaces/docs-writter ~/.openclaw/workspaces/security-auditor"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m56f5lff3ihq_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ln -sfn /home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry ~/.openclaw/workspaces/docs-writter/lookitry 2>/dev/null\nln -sfn /home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry ~/.openclaw/workspaces/security-auditor/lookitry 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":346,"output":453,"cacheRead":53824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54623,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776021662586,"responseId":"062b239efe349c90b865f865241b8a5b"}}
