{"type":"message","id":"a85cbe02","parentId":"4b67d16a","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:22:50.086Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me fix the EOF issue. The problem is the accented characters in the file. Let me write it differently.\n","thinkingSignature":"2fcd7946b3c14f1671d25baaac3c05ff4d42cb8c6468f0613bfbec9e74eea735"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0yk3tcqm3xjv_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Mensaje para Agentes - Auto-Identificacion\n\n**De:** Sam (Owner)\n**Fecha:** 2026-04-12\n**Prioridad:** Alta\n\n---\n\n## INSTRUCCION PARA CADA AGENTE\n\nCada agente debe responderse con:\n\n1. **Tu nombre corto** (para llamarte facilmente)\n2. **Tu emoji distintivo**\n3. **Una frase que te identifique** (como te describes en una linea)\n\n---\n\n## EJEMPLO:\n```\nNombre: \"Wizard\"\nEmoji: 🧙\nDescripcion: \"El especialista en frontend y UX de Lookitry\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## AGENTES QUE DEBEN RESPONDER:\n- WebWizard\n- DevGuardian\n- DataAlchemist\n- GrowthPilot\n- ArchitectAI\n- DocsWriter\n- SecurityAuditor\n\n**Responde en tu proximo turno activo.**\n\n---\n\n*Este mensaje sera ledo por cada agente en su proxima ejecucion.*","path":"/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/.shared-inbox/NOMBRE_AGENTES.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":316,"output":280,"cacheRead":55104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55700,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776021761674,"responseId":"062b2402220ed5b29d93400ae55c3b58"}}
