{"type":"message","id":"fa615a9c","parentId":"b53761ef","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:36:25.489Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The gateway is bound to localhost only (127.0.0.1), not to the Tailscale IP. This means you can only access it from the local machine, not remotely via Tailscale. I need to check if I can reconfigure it to bind to the Tailscale IP or all interfaces.\n","thinkingSignature":"fe345e99937dc8f663c629d5ae7151c0273840d0797c514fd3855284303d246b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n📊 **Diagnóstico completado, Sam:**\n\n| Componente | Status |\n|------------|--------|\n| Tailscale | ✅ Activo (IP: 100.85.125.102) |\n| OpenClaw Gateway | ✅ Corriendo en puerto 4002 |\n| **Acceso remoto** | ❌ **Solo localhost** |\n\n---\n\n### 🚨 PROBLEMA ENCONTRADO:\n\nEl gateway de OpenClaw está bindeado solo a `127.0.0.1` (localhost), **no a la IP de Tailscale**.\n\n```\n✅ curl localhost:4002 → OK\n❌ curl 100.85.125.102:4002 → FAIL\n```\n\n---\n\n### 🔧 SOLUCIÓN:\n\nPuedo cambiar la configuración del gateway para que escuche en todas las interfaces (0.0.0.0) o específicamente en la IP de Tailscale.\n\n**Quieres que lo habilite?** Necesito reiniciar el gateway después del cambio.\n\n**Opción recomendada:** Bind a `0.0.0.0` para que funcione desde cualquier red vía Tailscale.\n\n¿Procedo? 🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":191,"output":303,"cacheRead":79232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79726,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776022575048,"responseId":"062b272f3ba1bd18aa908a356e230f65"}}
