{"type":"message","id":"441d8b66","parentId":"6fcb29f8","timestamp":"2026-04-12T19:37:08.823Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sam is asking if we can continue working locally - just the two of us. He's fine with the current setup where the gateway only listens on localhost. This means he's not necessarily asking me to enable remote access right now - he just wants to confirm we can keep working together locally.\n\nI should confirm that yes, we can continue working together locally - that's exactly how we've been doing it. The control UI connects to localhost:4002 which is working fine.\n","thinkingSignature":"db944eef2477cce8d67079c9e9ec480ecccf8bdac6753c4b719d4681a0490ab4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**¡Sí, claro!** 🙌\n\nMientras estés en el mismo computador (localhost), tú y yo seguimos trabajando perfectamente — de hecho, **así es como estamos operando ahora mismo**.\n\n| Escenario | Status |\n|-----------|--------|\n| Tú → Control UI → localhost:4002 | ✅ Perfecto |\n| Yo → OpenClaw → Sammy (esta sesión) | ✅ Perfecto |\n| Tailscale → acceso externo | ❌ No configurado (no necesario) |\n\n---\n\n**Solo confirma:** ¿Quieres que deje todo como está (solo local) o prefieres tener también acceso remoto por Tailscale para cuando estés en otro lugar?\n\nPor ahora mantenemos el modo local que funciona. ¿Qué necesitas que haga, Sam? 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":369,"output":246,"cacheRead":79360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79975,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776022619196,"responseId":"062b275b503fc2773861773bc8ac773a"}}
