{"type":"message","id":"e80780dd","parentId":"f8765ed9","timestamp":"2026-04-12T20:51:29.276Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found the problem! Rebecca is stuck in a loop trying to send messages to Sammy via `sessions_send` but getting \"Agent-to-agent messaging denied by tools.agentToAgent.allow.\"\n\nThe config says `allow: ['sammy', 'rebecca']` which should work for short names, but maybe the system needs full session keys.\n\nLooking at the conversation, Rebecca tried many approaches to reach Sammy but keeps getting denied. She's now stuck in a thinking/loop state - her last message shows she's thinking about how to solve this.\n\nThe problem is:\n1. Rebecca is trying to communicate with Sammy via sessions_send\n2. The config has `allow: ['sammy', 'rebecca']` \n3. But the system is denying it\n\nThe fix should be to update the config to allow agent-to-agent between sammy and rebecca properly, or maybe restart the gateway to pick up the latest config changes.\n\nActually, looking at the logs:\n- \"Updated allow to full session keys\" and \"Reloaded\" - so Rebecca updated the config\n- But the gateway may need a full restart to pick up the new config\n\nLet me restart the gateway to force it to reload the config.\n","thinkingSignature":"42ab90c6ae9e90ca9089fcb7915fefebf529833afda4405d341ec0922059d4a8"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n🚨 **ENCONTRÉ EL PROBLEMA!**\n\nRebecca está **atrapada en un loop** intentando comunicarse conmigo (Sammy) via `sessions_send` pero el gateway **niega la conexión**.\n\n```\n\"Agent-to-agent messaging denied by tools.agentToAgent.allow\"\n```\n\nRebecca intentó fixing el config pero sigue sin funcionar.\n\n**Solución: Reiniciar el gateway para aplicar los cambios:**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d7zu8l5pa9ii_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sudo systemctl restart openclaw-gateway 2>/dev/null || systemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway 2>/dev/null || (kill -USR1 6623 && echo \"