{"type":"message","id":"0781203f","parentId":"7f0eed48","timestamp":"2026-04-12T20:51:51.845Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The gateway is already running and responding. The issue isn't with the gateway being down. The problem is that when I \"fixed\" the JSON earlier, I may have introduced a problem with the tools.agentToAgent configuration.\n\nLet me check the current state of the openclaw.json to see what the allow list looks like now.\n","thinkingSignature":"c511f9f14fa0fb20ba371ded5f5a757fde52eddb45b349ba6724e841ab19c7e7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n✅ **Gateway responding** — but I see the real problem now.\n\n---\n\n**🚨 DIAGNOSTICADO — Rebecca se quedó colgada por Configuration Chaos:**\n\n1. Ella intenta enviarme mensajes con `sessions_send` → **DENIED** (her config blocked)\n2. Mis cambios al JSON probablemente rompieron algo\n3. Rebecca está en loop intentando comunicarse conmigo\n\n---\n\n**¿Quieres que:**\n\n1. **Reviva Rebecca** — reinicio su sesión y le aviso que el problema está siendo solucionado\n2. **Revise el JSON** — verifico que `tools.agentToAgent.allow` esté correcto\n\n¿Cuál prefieres, Sam? 🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":159,"output":203,"cacheRead":76800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77162,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776027099363,"responseId":"062b38db3770ecd125f15dce818cc975"}}
