{"type":"message","id":"fef32dc9","parentId":"91e8c73b","timestamp":"2026-04-12T20:54:19.209Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good! Message sent to Sam (Ruben) through Rebecca's bot channel - this confirms the bot is working and can send messages. Let me summarize everything for Sam.\n","thinkingSignature":"2815d30bd180e029fa25c7a6bd6ffc4e42306045f81a7a53346bde5ffccb08b9"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n✅ **TAREAS COMPLETADAS!**\n\n---\n\n## 📋 RESUMEN:\n\n| Tarea | Status | Detalle |\n|-------|--------|---------|\n| **1. Verificar JSON** | ✅ | `tools.agentToAgent.allow = [\"agent:sammy:main\", \"agent:rebecca:main\"]` — Config correcto |\n| **2. Revivir Rebecca** | ✅ | Lock removido, Gateway reiniciado, mensaje enviado |\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 Configuración Actual:\n\n```\ntools.agentToAgent.allow: \n  - agent:sammy:main\n  - agent:rebecca:main\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📱 Prueba:\n\nMensaje enviado a Telegram (chat Sam Wilkie via Rebecca bot): \n> \"Rebecca! Soy Sammy. El problema de comunicación fue solucionado...\"\n\n**Si Rebecca aún está colgada**, puede que necesite cerrar y reabrir el chat en Telegram para resetear su estado.\n\n¿Qué ves desde tu lado, Sam? 🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":173,"output":233,"cacheRead":97344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97750,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776027253216,"responseId":"062b39751f143dee63d633c5021247c8"}}
