{"type":"message","id":"33fffabc","parentId":"1b9d7123","timestamp":"2026-04-12T20:56:43.604Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me also note that the lock file in Sam's session might be an issue too. But I already tried to remove it. Let me also think about what else could cause Rebecca to be \"stuck writing\". It could be that:\n\n1. Rebecca's session file has a lock\n2. The gateway is overloaded processing many concurrent sessions\n3. There's a tool that's taking too long\n\nLet me check if there are any long-running tools in Rebecca's session.\n\nActually, looking at the previous output, Rebecca was trying to communicate with Sammy using sessions_send and getting denied. The gateway fix should help. But if Rebecca is still stuck, it might be that she needs to restart her Telegram conversation or there's a UI-level issue.\n\nLet me just inform Sam of the progress.\n","thinkingSignature":"a14e89c0de177903223fe81d968677f0d882088a66ef495d5628319dc5bd131e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n\n✅ **Fix aplicado!**\n\n| Cambio | Valor Anterior | Valor Ahora |\n|--------|----------------|-------------|\n| `tools.agentToAgent.allow` | `[\"agent:sammy:main\", \"agent:rebecca:main\"]` (full session keys) | `[\"sammy\", \"rebecca\"]` (simple IDs) |\n\n---\n\n📱 **Mensaje enviado a Rebecca** informándole del fix.\n\n---\n\n**Si Rebecca sigue colgada**, puede ser por:\n1. **Telegram UI bug** — debe cerrar y reabrir el chat\n2. **Sesión corrupta** — necesita que Rebecca envíe `/start` para resetear\n\n¿Puedes pedirle que cierre el chat de Rebecca en Telegram y lo reabra? 🔄"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":206,"output":314,"cacheRead":100928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101448,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776027390019,"responseId":"062b39fe2e98f06d0548053f40393368"}}
