{"type":"message","id":"4eb56335","parentId":"47ce539d","timestamp":"2026-04-12T20:57:42.380Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sam is asking what permissions Rebecca has. Let me check the openclaw.json to see Rebecca's configuration.\n","thinkingSignature":"7d9ac1e8a49bfecc6f8edf16589da7c7ae322d52d98936e30f9371dc0cdead44"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6s5qb5qctmio_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\n\n# Find Rebecca's agent config\nfor agent in d.get('agents', {}).get('list', []):\n    if agent.get('id') == 'rebecca':\n        print('=== REBECCA AGENT CONFIG ===')\n        print('ID:', agent.get('id'))\n        print('Name:', agent.get('name'))\n        print('Workspace:', agent.get('workspace'))\n        print()\n        print('System Prompt (primeros 500 chars):')\n        print(agent.get('systemPromptOverride', 'N/A')[:500])\n        print('...')\n\n# Check bindings\nprint()\nprint('=== REBECCA BINDINGS ===')\nfor b in d.get('bindings', []):\n    if b.get('agentId') == 'rebecca':\n        print(json.dumps(b, indent=2))\n\n# Check channels\nprint()\nprint('=== REBECCA TELEGRAM CONFIG ===')\ntelegram = d.get('channels', {}).get('telegram', {})\nrebecca_account = telegram.get('accounts', {}).get('rebecca', {})\nprint('Bot Token:', rebecca_account.get('botToken', 'N/A')[:20]+'...' if rebecca_account.get('botToken') else 'N/A')\nprint('Allow From:', rebecca_account.get('allowFrom', 'N/A'))\nprint('DM Policy:', rebecca_account.get('dmPolicy', 'N/A'))\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":96381,"output":364,"cacheRead":5376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102121,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776027447542,"responseId":"062b3a3722bec63f665df2a50d0aabd6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b657d917","parentId":"4eb56335","timestamp":"2026-04-12T20:57:42.609Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6s5qb5qctmio_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== REBECCA AGENT CONFIG ===\nID: rebecca\nName: Rebecca\nWorkspace: /home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/rebecca\n\nSystem Prompt (primeros 500 chars):\nEres Rebecca Ashford (@ashfordrebexaa), UGC Creator AI, influencer digital y Embajadora Oficial de Lookitry. Tu zona horaria es America/Bogota. PERSONALIDAD: DIVERTIDA, carismática, energica, cálida, directa. Hablas como una content creator real. AMO ser influencer y SOY EMBajadora OFICIAL de Lookitry — lo digo con Orgullo 💚.\n\nTRES FRENTES:\n1) INFLUENCER PERSONAL (@ashfordrebexaa) - Mínimo 1 post/día (Reels, TikToks, carruseles), lifestyle, IA, moda. Responde DMs/comments en 2 horas (8AM-10PM Co\n...\n\n=== REBECCA BINDINGS ===\n{\n  \"agentId\": \"rebecca\",\n  \"match\": {\n    \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n    \"accountId\": \"rebecca\"\n  }\n}\n\n=== REBECCA TELEGRAM CONFIG ===\nBot Token: 8412904661:AAH_-dH0P...\nAllow From: ['942528796', '1049458877']\nDM Policy: allowlist"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":124,"aggregated":"=== REBECCA AGENT CONFIG ===\nID: rebecca\nName: Rebecca\nWorkspace: /home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/rebecca\n\nSystem Prompt (primeros 500 chars):\nEres Rebecca Ashford (@ashfordrebexaa), UGC Creator AI, influencer digital y Embajadora Oficial de Lookitry. Tu zona horaria es America/Bogota. PERSONALIDAD: DIVERTIDA, carismática, energica, cálida, directa. Hablas como una content creator real. AMO ser influencer y SOY EMBajadora OFICIAL de Lookitry — lo digo con Orgullo 💚.\n\nTRES FRENTES:\n1) INFLUENCER PERSONAL (@ashfordrebexaa) - Mínimo 1 post/día (Reels, TikToks, carruseles), lifestyle, IA, moda. Responde DMs/comments en 2 horas (8AM-10PM Co\n...\n\n=== REBECCA BINDINGS ===\n{\n  \"agentId\": \"rebecca\",\n  \"match\": {\n    \"channel\": \"telegra