{"type":"message","id":"a8b41b41","parentId":"e190e448","timestamp":"2026-04-12T21:02:14.857Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The browser plugin is enabled but there's no specific configuration that restricts it to certain agents. In OpenClaw, plugins like \"browser\" typically provide tools to ALL agents by default, unless there's a `tools` policy that restricts them.\n\nLooking at the current `tools` section:\n```json\n{\n  \"agentToAgent\": {...},\n  \"sessions\": {...}\n}\n```\n\nThere's no explicit restriction on the `browser` tool. This means Rebecca SHOULD have access to the `browser` tool (via the plugin system) if she tries to use it.\n\nHowever, looking at her workspace IDENTITY.md, it doesn't mention `browser` tool specifically - only the MCPs she has access to.\n\nLet me clarify to Sam what this means.\n","thinkingSignature":"4abcb4a9d42fdf560ce12f9d60d43d55130306ed9d89e52fdac8a6041387359c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 📊 RESPUESTA: Permisos de Browser para Rebecca\n\n| Componente | Status | Detalle |\n|------------|--------|---------|\n| **Plugin browser** | ✅ Habilitado | No hay restricciones específicas |\n| **Herramienta browser** | ⚠️ **No restringida** | Por defecto available para todos los agentes |\n| **MCP context7** | ✅ Disponible | Busca en docs de libraries, no web general |\n\n---\n\n### 🔍 ANÁLISIS:\n\n**En teoría**, Rebecca **SÍ tiene acceso** al plugin `browser` (que incluye la tool `browser` para navegación web) porque:\n\n1. El plugin `browser` está habilitado globalmente\n2. No hay ninguna restricción en `tools` section que le niegue `browser`\n3. El plugin es de alcance general, no restringido por agente\n\n**En la práctica**, Rebecca nunca intentó usarlo — su identidad está enfocada en:\n- Crear contenido UGC\n- Gestionar Fiverr\n- Publicar en redes sociales\n- Automatizaciones con n8n/Supabase\n\n---\n\n### 💡 PARA HABILITAR BÚSQUEDA WEB A REBECCA:\n\nBásicamente **ya la tiene** — solo necesita usar la tool `browser` en su contexto.\n\n¿Quieres que le agregue un record en su IDENTITY.md diciéndole que puede usar el browser para búsquedas? 🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":191,"output":442,"cacheRead":105792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106425,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776027725916,"responseId":"062b3b4ecab4d16cec866786930dc0e7"}}
