{"type":"message","id":"303a35e7","parentId":"1a49063b","timestamp":"2026-04-12T21:04:50.637Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - Tailscale Serve is running. Now Sam can access via the Tailscale hostname from any device connected to the same tailnet.\n","thinkingSignature":"7eb5a6b0d313736c60d36f9046226b1ed4b163ecba7df498e74cb1cfd2a21120"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n✅ **Tailscale Serve ACTIVADO!**\n\n---\n\n## 🌐 ACCESO DESDE TU PC EN REMOTO\n\n### Opción 1: Tailscale (recomendado)\n\nDesde cualquier dispositivo conectado a tu tailnet:\n\n```\nhttps://travis-system-product-name.tailfcaac6.ts.net/\n```\n\n**Token:** `fca2235a378d3882993e733b5b15b729`\n\n---\n\n### Opción 2: IP directa (si conoces la IP de Tailscale)\n\n```\nhttps://100.85.125.102:4002/\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📋 REQUISITOS:\n\n1. **Tailscale instalado** en tu PC de casa\n2. **Sesión de Tailscale iniciada** con tu cuenta `samwilkiedevs@`\n3. **Mismo tailnet** (tu cuenta debe estar autorizada)\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 Si NO tienes Tailscale en tu PC:\n\n1. Descarga Tailscale desde https://tailscale.com/download\n2. Instala e inicia sesión con tu cuenta\n3. Conéctate a la misma red que este servidor\n4. Abre `https://travis-system-product-name.tailfcaac6.ts.net/`\n\n---\n\n**¿Tienes Tailscale instalado en tu PC de casa, Sam?** Si no, te guío paso a paso. 🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":175,"output":315,"cacheRead":107392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107882,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776027883004,"responseId":"062b3beb883d80b7261ced45045b955e"}}
