{"type":"message","id":"7a4887cb","parentId":"7c520abd","timestamp":"2026-04-12T21:06:16.520Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sam is trying to access the Tailscale serve URL but it's not opening. Let me help him troubleshoot. The issues could be:\n\n1. The URL requires the token for authentication\n2. Tailscale might not be properly configured on his end\n3. He needs to use the token in the URL\n\nLet me explain how to properly access it and check if there's an auth issue.\n","thinkingSignature":"117da1a1cb6301f36f277bfaa27e2345098a6a9f3d296340d42c36418a75ec5d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nEntiendo, Sam. El acceso requiere **autenticación con el token**.\n\n---\n\n## 🔐 ACCESO CORRECTO:\n\nHay 2 formas:\n\n### Forma 1 — Con token en header ( navegador):\n```\nhttps://travis-system-product-name.tailfcaac6.ts.net/\n```\n\nLuego cuando pida contraseña/token, usas:\n```\nToken: fca2235a378d3882993e733b5b15b729\n```\n\n### Forma 2 — Directo en URL (no recomendado, solo para prueba):\n```\nhttps://fca2235a378d3882993e733b5b15b729@travis-system-product-name.tailfcaac6.ts.net/\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 ¿Dónde conseguir la IP de Tailscale?\n\n**Desde tu PC de casa:**\n\n1. **Windows/Mac:** Abre Terminal y escribe:\n   ```\n   tailscale ip\n   ```\n\n2. **Si no tienes Tailscale instalado:**\n   - Descárgalo de: https://tailscale.com/download\n   - Instálalo y conecta con tu cuenta\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ POSIBLES PROBLEMAS:\n\n1. **Tailscale Serve caiu** — Voy a verificar\n2. **Token no funciona** — Puede que el gateway haya hecho reload y cambiado algo\n\nDéjame verificar el estado:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i77jnoafwqls_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -v --connect-timeout 5 https://travis-system-product-name.tailfcaac6.ts.net/health 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":494,"output":409,"cacheRead":107520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108423,"cost":{"