{"type":"message","id":"0a7aa12c","parentId":"63afb1c3","timestamp":"2026-04-12T21:06:25.402Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The HTTPS connection works from within the server. But Sam says it doesn't open in his browser. This could be because:\n\n1. He's not on the tailnet (Tailscale not connected on his PC)\n2. The browser is blocking the self-signed cert\n3. The gateway is rejecting the connection due to auth\n\nLet me check the token issue and see if we need to send the token properly.\n\nAlso, the domain `travis-system-product-name.tailfcaac6.ts.net` resolves to `100.85.125.102` which is the Tailscale IP. That's the IP Sam asked about.\n\nLet me help Sam with:\n1. Getting Tailscale on his PC\n2. Making sure the browser accepts the cert or using the token properly\n","thinkingSignature":"29d10ffc32b7666b23d6ca031c3ef13c189a3ba2f6db2a0f1e7db7efb2c05f89"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nEl enlace **SÍ funciona** desde el servidor. El problema es probablemente:\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 PROBLEMA 1: No estás conectado a Tailscale desde tu PC\n\n**La IP de Tailscale de este servidor es:** `100.85.125.102`\n\nPero para acceder, **tu PC también necesita Tailscale conectado**.\n\n---\n\n## 📋 CÓMO CONECTAR DESDE TU PC:\n\n### Paso 1: Descargar Tailscale\n- **Windows/Mac**: https://tailscale.com/download\n- **Linux**: `sudo apt install tailscale`\n\n### Paso 2: Iniciar sesión\n```bash\ntailscale up\n```\nTe dará un enlace para autenticar en el navegador.\n\n### Paso 3: Conectar\nUna vez que Tailscale esté activo en tu PC, puedes acceder a:\n```\nhttps://travis-system-product-name.tailfcaac6.ts.net/\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 PROBLEMA 2: Token de autenticación\n\nEl gateway tiene **token obrigatório**. Debes añadirlo:\n\n```\nhttps://travis-system-product-name.tailfcaac6.ts.net/?token=fca2235a378d3882993e733b5b15b729\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 Alternativa rápida (sin Tailscale):\n\nSi quieres acceso **sin Tailscale**, necesitaríamos abrir el puerto 4002 en el firewall o usar otro método.\n\n**¿Ya tienes Tailscale instalado en tu PC de casa, Sam?** 🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":546,"output":468,"cacheRead":107968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108982,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776027976765,"responseId":"062b3c490a49bc17225ddf3cf49b2601"}}
