{"type":"message","id":"41ca2706","parentId":"a8932c21","timestamp":"2026-04-12T21:08:57.632Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sam's Tailscale IP is 100.75.120.122 and my server's Tailscale IP is 100.85.125.102. Both are on the same tailnet, so they should be able to communicate.\n\nThe issue might be that the gateway isn't listening on the Tailscale interface, or the firewall is blocking the connection. Let me check if the server is actually listening on the Tailscale IP and test connectivity.\n","thinkingSignature":"da2be091320e1fa6a312bc307b6818477222fd0131c32d691a977228c03c6fc0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nPerfecto! 🎯 **Ahora los tenemos:**\n\n| Dispositivo | IP Tailscale |\n|--------------|--------------|\n| **Tu PC (Sam)** | `100.75.120.122` |\n| **Servidor (Sammy)** | `100.85.125.102` |\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 Primero verifico si el servidor está escuchando correctamente:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lehqhes5dyt0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ss -tlnp | grep 4002"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lehqhes5dyt0_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --connect-timeout 3 http://100.85.125.102:4002/health 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":483,"output":246,"cacheRead":108928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109657,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776028130073,"responseId":"062b3ce2b8a689323ff84709e4cf757c"}}
