{"type":"message","id":"d9d08515","parentId":"2a02fdf8","timestamp":"2026-04-12T21:26:50.393Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1026\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1049458877\",\n  \"sender\": \"Wilkie Devs & Design\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-12 16:26 GMT-5\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Wilkie Devs & Design (1049458877)\",\n  \"id\": \"1049458877\",\n  \"name\": \"Wilkie Devs & Design\",\n  \"username\": \"WilkieDevs\"\n}\n```\n\nPodrías pedirle al equipo que verifique en que etapa se encuentra el proyecto de lookitry?"}],"timestamp":1776029210343}}
{"type":"message","id":"c5b2f93a","parentId":"d9d08515","timestamp":"2026-04-12T21:27:07.981Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sam wants me to ask the team (agents) about the current status of the Lookitry project. I should spawn the relevant agents and ask them to report on their respective areas.\n\nThe team is:\n- Carlos (WebWizard) - Frontend\n- Diego (DevGuardian) - Security\n- Luis (DataAlchemist) - DB/IA\n- Esteban (GrowthPilot) - Marketing/CRM\n- Álvaro (ArchitectAI) - Infrastructure\n- Doc (DocsWriter) - Documentation\n- Marcus (SecurityAuditor) - Security audit\n\nI should spawn all of them asking for a status update on their respective areas of the Lookitry project.\n","thinkingSignature":"a5cb34f3700aa55212e0291f15d2970c73f3a94f85b9c6da514ba46a5f7d239e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qqavnwwdqg0t_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"mode":"run","runtime":"subagent","task":"Eres Carlos (alias WebWizard) de Lookitry. Sam (el owner) quiere un reporte de estado.\n\nTu área: Frontend - UI/UX, Next.js, widget Try-On, /pruebalo/, /embed/, /sitio/, /dashboard/\n\nResponde con:\n1. Qué está hecho\n2. Qué está en progreso  \n3. Qué falta\n4. Bloqueos o problemas\n\nSé Conciso y claro. Solo reporta tu área.","timeoutSeconds":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qqavnwwdqg0t_2","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"mode":"run","runtime":"subagent","task":"Eres Diego (alias DevGuardian) de Lookitry. Sam (el owner) quiere un reporte de estado.\n\nTu área: Seguridad, pagos (Wompi/PayPal), JWT, webhooks, testing\n\nResponde con:\n1. Qué está hecho\n2. Qué está en progreso\n3. Qué falta\n4. Bloqueos o problemas\n\nSé Conciso y claro. Solo reporta tu área.","timeoutSeconds":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qqavnwwdqg0t_3","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"mode":"run","runtime":"subagent","task":"Eres Luis (alias DataAlchemist) de Lookitry. Sam (el owner) quiere un reporte de estado.\n\nTu área: DB/