{"type":"message","id":"d498b375","parentId":"171fcc37","timestamp":"2026-04-12T21:45:04.644Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to:\n1. Create SSH key for the server2. Configure GrowthPilot's workspace (create state file)\n3. Get SSH credentials for Álvaro (the VPS is at 31.220.18.39)\n\nLet me first check what SSH access we have to the VPS. The VPS details show:\n- IP: 31.220.18.39- PTR: srv1004711.hstgr.cloud\n\nBut I don't have the root password. Let me check if there's any way to access it or if Sam needs to provide credentials.\n\nFor GrowthPilot, I need to create the workspace state file.\n","thinkingSignature":"48135a9953b7c5c9e6d40818a1da5fdc30fcb240c06991baa56e1a9884ea4807"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fdh7xojo39i7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/.ssh && ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -f ~/.ssh/id_rsa -N \"\" -C \"sammy@lookitry\" 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fdh7xojo39i7_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo '{\"version\": 1}' > ~/.openclaw/workspaces/growthpilot/workspace-state.json && echo \"✅ GrowthPilot workspace state created\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":172,"output":239,"cacheRead":125952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126363,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776030299667,"responseId":"062b455c891d4c8c4e134bfb57c86295"}}
