{"type":"message","id":"a2e187a1","parentId":"344787dc","timestamp":"2026-04-12T21:45:35.060Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, now I need to share the SSH public key with Sam so he can add it to the VPS. Let me create a message with the SSH key for Álvaro (ArchitectAI).\n","thinkingSignature":"bbd5ac7ae2fdef8508e3507283e3886db87b24ef089e10b706a0609e21fd7f79"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n✅ **Workpaces configurados y SSH key creado!**\n\n---\n\n## 📋 CONFIGURACIÓN COMPLETADA:\n\n| Agente | Workspace | Estado |\n|--------|-----------|--------|\n| ✅ GrowthPilot (Esteban) | `/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry` | State file creado |\n| ✅ ArchitectAI (Álvaro) | `/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry` | State file creado |\n| ✅ DataAlchemist (Luis) | `/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry` | State file creado |\n| ✅ SSH Key | Generada en `~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub` | Lista para usar |\n\n---\n\n## 🔑 SSH KEY PARA ALVARO (ArchitectAI):\n\n```\nssh-rsa  sammy@lookitry\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📋 LO QUE NECESITA ALVARO (VPS credentials):\n\n**IP del VPS:** `31.220.18.39`  \n**Hostname:** `wilkiedevs.com`  \n**SSH Key:** La clave pública de arriba\n\n**Para agregar la SSH key al VPS, Sam necesita:**\n\n1. Ir a Hostinger → VPS → SSH Keys\n2. Agregar la clave pública de arriba\n3. O conectarte manualmente al VPS y agregar la key a `~/.ssh/authorized_keys`\n\n---\n\n**¿Quieres que guarde estas configuraciones en un archivo para referencia, Sam?** 🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":650,"output":599,"cacheRead":126400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127649,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776030321679,"responseId":"062b4572404a4f201d0ec8507f338041"}}
