{"type":"compaction","id":"ae4d1378","parentId":"f677efaa","timestamp":"2026-04-12T22:05:32.718Z","summary":"## Goal\n- Apply project recommendations (HSTS, JWT logout, CSRF, skeleton loaders, testimonials) without breaking anything\n- Delegate tasks to specialized agents (DevGuardian, WebWizard, DataAlchemist, ArchitectAI)\n- Resolve remote access to OpenClaw via Tailscale for Sam\n- Complete brainstorming session with team before implementing\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Sam must approve designs before any implementation (brainstorming HARD-GATE)\n- Credentials must remain private (SSH keys, VPS IP not exposed in chat)\n- No code changes until safety verified by agents\n- Sam's identity: Sam Wilkie, Owner/Founder of Lookitry, Developer at Wilkie Devs\n- Remote access via Tailscale: Sam's IP 100.75.120.122, Server IP 100.85.125.102\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Fixed openclaw.json config corruption (agentToAgent allow list)\n- [x] Created SSH key at ~/.ssh/id_rsa for production access\n- [x] Configured workspaces for GrowthPilot, ArchitectAI, DataAlchemist\n- [x] Updated Rebecca's IDENTITY.md with browser tool access\n- [x] Spawned 3 agents for security/UX investigation\n- [x] Received DevGuardian (Diego) security report\n- [x] Received WebWizard (Carlos) skeleton loaders report\n- [x] Created LOG_SISTEMA.md verifying development environment\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Awaiting DataAlchemist (Luis) report on DB schema\n- [ ] Awaiting third round of agent responses from earlier status requests\n\n### Blocked\n- Álvaro (ArchitectAI) needs SSH credentials to production VPS\n- Luis (DataAlchemist) needs schema confirmation from Sam\n- Remote access via Tailscale not fully working for Sam\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **GitHub access**: Repo is https://github.com/depper-IA/Lookitry, pull-only (no push credentials configured)\n- **Frontend dev**: Next.js dev server at localhost:3000 (not currently running)\n- **Security fixes marked DELICADO**: JWT blacklist requires multi-file changes, CSRF tokens require full-stack changes\n- **HSTS is safe to implement** only after validating all subdomains serve HTTPS\n- **Skeleton loaders are SAFE** to add (additive-only, no breaking changes)\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Wait for DataAlchemist (Luis) report on DB schema\n2. Present WebWizard's skeleton loader implementation plan to Sam for approval\n3. Present DevGuardian's HSTS implementation (low effort, safe if domains verified)\n4. Escalate JWT blacklist and CSRF tokens as separate long-term projects\n5. Help Sam connect to Tailscale for remote access\n6. Start local dev server if Sam wants to preview changes\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Security findings**: HSTS ❌, JWT blacklist ❌, CSRF tokens ❌\n- **Security positives**: Rate limiting ✅, Turnstile ✅, HTTP-only cookies ✅, CSP ✅\n- **Skeleton findings**: GenerationLoader exists but for TryOn only; LandingReviews and ReviewsSlider have no loading state\n- **Frontend files**: `/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/frontend/src/components/landing/new-landing/`\n- **Backend files**: `/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/backend/src/services/auth.service.ts`\n- **VPS**: IP 31.220.18.39, hostname wilkiedevs.com\n- **Agent team**: 8 agents configured in openclaw.json with workspaces\n- **Tailscale serve URL**: https://travis-system-product-name.tailfcaac6.ts.net/ (working but Sam's DNS not resolving)\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n\n\n## Original Request\nSammy received notification that DataAlchemist (Luis) timed out while investigating the Supabase DB schema per Sam's request. Luis's task was to review the current schema (tables: brands, products, subscriptions, pricing_config), check migration files, and compare against the PRD.\n\n## Early Progress\n- Luis's subagent timed out with no output\n- Sammy detected the timeout, decided to do a quick manual check\n- Ran two exec commands to inspect migrations directory and grep for key table references\n- Tool results showed 18 migration files (ranging from 20260318 to 20260406) and grep matches highlighting brands table references (internal_notes, referrals), pricing_config, products, and subscriptions\n\n## Context for Suffix\nSammy's immediate check revealed active migrations exist for brands, pricing_config, and referrals program. The suffix likely contains Sammy's response to Sam summarizing: (1) Luis's timeout, (2) what the quick migration scan uncovered, and (3) what needs Sam's confirmation given the incomplete picture.\n\n<read-files>\n/home/travis/.openclaw/config-health.json\n/home/travis/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/HEARTBEAT.md\n/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/Lookitry_Brain_Vault/Cerebro/Skills/brainstorming.md\n/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/architectai/IDENTITY.md\n/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/dataalchemist/IDENTITY.md\n/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/devguardian/IDENTITY.md\n/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/docs-writter/IDENTITY.md\n/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/growthpilot/IDENTITY.md\n/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/security-auditor/IDENTITY.md\n/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/webwizard/IDENTITY.md\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/.shared-inbox/NOMBRE_AGENTES.md\n/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/LOG_SISTEMA.md\n/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/rebecca/IDENTITY.md\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"251a0838","tokensBefore":167922,"details":{"readFiles":["/home/travis/.openclaw/config-health.json","/home/travis/.openclaw/openclaw.json","/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/HEARTBEAT.md","/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/Lookitry_Brain_Vault/Cerebro/Skills/brainstorming.md","/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/architectai/IDENTITY.md","/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/dataalchemist/IDENTITY.md","/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/devguardian/IDENTITY.md","/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/docs-writter/IDENTITY.md","/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/growthpilot/IDENTITY.md","/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/security-auditor/IDENTITY.md","/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/webwizard/IDENTITY.md"],"modifiedFiles":["/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/.shared-inbox/NOMBRE_AGENTES.md","/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/LOG_SISTEMA.md","/home/travis/Lookitry/Lookitry/rebecca/IDENTITY.md"]},"fromHook":false}
