{"type":"message","id":"186dbced","parentId":"15ddcaee","timestamp":"2026-04-12T22:07:22.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Redis is not installed locally. Let me check the backend health again - earlier it showed redis as \"disconnected\". That's the issue - the backend needs Redis for session management.\n\nAlso, the user mentioned they can't access \"el dashboard de usuario\" - let me check if the backend is having Redis issues which could be causing the dashboard to not load properly.","thinkingSignature":"b9da1549dadd991b747466a68784aeb716b845cae59f6b63ab54b51b4737762e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**Redis NO está instalado** — lo detecté antes:\n\n```\n\"redis\":{\"status\":\"disconnected\"}\n```\n\nEl backend **no puede** almacenar sesiones sin Redis. Por eso el dashboard no carga para ti.\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 SOLUCIÓN RÁPIDA:\n\n```bash\n# Instalar Redis\nsudo apt update && sudo apt install redis-server -y\n\n# Iniciar Redis\nsudo systemctl start redis\nsudo systemctl enable redis\n\n# Verificar\nredis-cli ping\n# Debe responder: PONG\n```\n\n**Luego reinicia el backend:**\n```bash\ncd ~/Lookitry/Lookitry/backend\n# Si está con pm2:\npm2 restart lookitry-backend\n# O Ctrl+C y reinicia\n```\n\n---\n\n**¿Quieres que instale Redis ahora?** 🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":202,"output":236,"cacheRead":77216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77654,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776031638718,"responseId":"062b4a9786178e32da9d77f4da9f7b85"}}
