{"type":"message","id":"50cdeed5","parentId":"81d4a2a5","timestamp":"2026-04-12T22:31:15.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No hay credenciales para GitHub push. Sam配置了SSH key但没有配置Git credential。GitHub需要token或用户名密码来push。我们需要让Sam知道这个问题。","thinkingSignature":"13c7df744f510aaed0efea7c65abcafdfee6824cf31fb534f8bbb6bd78c0da45"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n⚠️ **No hay credenciales de GitHub configuradas para push.**\n\nEl repo es de **@depper-IA** — necesitas agregar un **GitHub Personal Access Token** para poder pushear.\n\n---\n\n### 🔧 OPCIÓN 1 - Configurar token:\n\n```bash\ngit remote set-url origin https://TU_TOKEN@github.com/depper-IA/Lookitry.git\ngit push origin main\n```\n\n### 📋 OPCIÓN 2 - Agregar como secret en OpenClaw:\n\nNecesito que me proporciones un **GitHub PAT** con permisos de `repo` para configurarlo.\n\n---\n\n**¿Tienes un token de GitHub o prefieres que simplemente hagas el push manualmente desde tu terminal?** 🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":154,"output":189,"cacheRead":113952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114295,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776033065498,"responseId":"062b5029cb4101449744a17952300e98"}}
