{"type":"message","id":"b334e5d8","parentId":"8d65e81d","timestamp":"2026-04-12T22:34:19.591Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sam wants me to audit the templates using WebWizard (Carlos) and the project's skills. I need to follow the brainstorming protocol - this is a creative work that requires design approval BEFORE implementation.\n\nLet me understand what Sam wants:\n1. Audit the mini-landing templates (Classic, Editorial, Moderno)\n2. Improve them in all senses: SEO, UI/UX, etc.\n\nFollowing the brainstorming skill, I need to:\n1. Explore project context (partially done)\n2. Offer visual companion (since this involves visual questions)\n3. Ask clarifying questions one at a time\n4. Propose approaches\n5. Present design and get approval\n6. Write design doc\n7. Get user review\n8. Then invoke writing-plans\n\nLet me start by exploring more context about the templates and then offer the visual companion.\n","thinkingSignature":"d7c86f846ff35d949b72071ee1d917df36f6c4a767b2f0c2a11222c99a195488"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nSiguiendo el protocolo de **brainstorming** — esto es trabajo creativo que requiere diseño antes de implementación.\n\n---\n\n## 🎨 AUDITORÍA DE TEMPLATES - CONTEXTO\n\n### 📋 Templates existentes:\n\n| Template | Líneas | Propósito |\n|---------|-------|----------|\n| `TemplateClassic` | 409 | Minimal/Bare |\n| `TemplateEditorial` | 328 | Estilo editorial |\n| `TemplateModerno` | 262 | Moderno/Minimal |\n\n### 🔍 Áreas a auditar:\n\n| Categoría | Items |\n|----------|-------|\n| **SEO** | Meta tags, OG, estructura headings, semántica |\n| **UI/UX** | Conversión, CTAs, mobile-first, accesibilidad |\n| **Rendimiento** | Imágenes, lazy loading, Core Web Vitals |\n| **Accesibilidad** | ARIA, contraste, focus states |\n| **Diseño** | Consistencia visual, tipografía, spacing |\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 PREGUNTA INICIAL:\n\n**¿Cuántos templates quieres mejorar?**\n\n- **A) Solo 1 template** (el más importante, para MVP rápido)\n- **B) 2 templates** (Classic + Moderno o Editorial)\n- **C) Los 3 templates** (auditoría completa)\n\n**Recomendación:** Empezar con **B) 2 templates** — Classic (más usado) + uno de los otros. ¿Cuál prefieres para comenzar? 🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1006,"output":478,"cacheRead":117568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119052,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776033250270,"responseId":"062b50e281247f5450c3c9a913e3dc90"}}
