{"type":"message","id":"d720b6bc","parentId":"927b453f","timestamp":"2026-04-12T22:39:23.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to self-review the spec inline per the brainstorming protocol, then show it to Sam for approval before proceeding.\n\nLet me do a quick self-review:\n\n1. **Placeholder scan:** Everything looks concrete, no TBD or TODO\n2. **Internal consistency:** All sections align, architecture matches descriptions\n3. **Scope check:** Focused on 3 templates, single implementation plan sized correctly\n4. **Ambiguity check:** Requirements are explicit\n\nThe spec looks good. Now I need to ask Sam to review it before I proceed to implementation.","thinkingSignature":"e4b2ff289ee1bfa5058b9af58e3962d1e2169a2f8796147eddb795ba1870f066"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ SPEC ESCRITO\n\n```\ndocs/superpowers/specs/2026-04-12-mini-landing-templates-audit-design.md\n```\n\n---\n\n### 📋 Resumen del Spec:\n\n| Área | Cambios | Prioridad |\n|------|---------|----------|\n| **SEO** | OpenGraph dinámico + JSON-LD Schema.org/Product | 🔴 Alta |\n| **UX** | Skeleton loaders + microinteracciones hover | 🔴 Alta |\n| **UI** | Animaciones de entrada suaves | 🟡 Media |\n| **A11y** | Focus rings + aria-labels | 🔴 Alta |\n| **Perf** | Lazy loading con Next/Image + blur placeholder | 🔴 Alta |\n\n**Tiempo estimado:** ~3 horas | **Riesgo:** Mínimo\n\n---\n\n**Por favor revisa el spec y dime si quieres hacer cambios antes de proceder con la implementación.**\n\n> 📄 Spec en: `docs/superpowers/specs/2026-04-12-mini-landing-templates-audit-design.md`\n\n🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2320,"output":333,"cacheRead":133088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135741,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776033557447,"responseId":"062b521556930411df887bf68f1baf1a"}}
