{"type":"message","id":"575d995a","parentId":"6a2b2cd4","timestamp":"2026-04-12T22:47:02.828Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All done. Let me give Sam a summary of what was completed.","thinkingSignature":"c873e96383eaa2bc755605dcfea4982bcd610912ec24fca218c772d6a62e2f23"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ IMPLEMENTACIÓN COMPLETADA — Opción A\n\n### 📦 Cambios aplicados:\n\n| Categoría | Cambio | Archivo |\n|----------|--------|---------|\n| **SEO** | OpenGraph dinámico (title, description, og:image, og:url) | `MiniLanding.tsx` |\n| **SEO** | JSON-LD Schema.org/Product | `MiniLanding.tsx` |\n| **SEO** | Twitter cards + meta description | `MiniLanding.tsx` |\n| **UX** | Skeleton loaders (3 skeletons mientras cargan productos) | `TemplateClassic.tsx` |\n| **Performance** | `sizes` attribute en todas las imágenes (Next/Image optimization) | 3 templates |\n| **Accesibilidad** | `focus-visible` rings en botones de productos | `TemplateClassic.tsx` |\n| **Shared** | `useScrollReveal` hook reutilizable | `shared.tsx` |\n| **Shared** | `ProductSkeleton` componente reutilizable | `shared.tsx` |\n\n### 📊 Estado del Spec:\n```\ndocs/superpowers/specs/2026-04-12-mini-landing-templates-audit-design.md\n```\n\n- ✅ OpenGraph tags\n- ✅ JSON-LD schema\n- ✅ Skeleton loading\n- ✅ Lazy loading + sizes\n- ✅ Focus rings\n- ⬜ aria-labels (pendiente)\n- ⬜ Scroll reveal animations (pendiente)\n- ⬜ Microinteracciones hover (pendiente)\n\n### 🚀 Commits:\n- `5995809` — feat(mini-landing): Opción A\n- `a34712a` — docs: actualizar spec\n\n**¿Continuamos con los pendientes o pasas a otra cosa?** 🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":180,"output":384,"cacheRead":81632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82196,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776034018351,"responseId":"062b53e22c68fcc10101ff9cac1c1219"}}
